msgstr "Vmesnik in vrata za vezavo"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:269
#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:732
msgid "Tunnel auto-start"
msgstr "Samodejni zagon tunelja"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:279
msgid "Wizard completed"
msgstr "Vodnik je končan"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:291
msgid ""
"This wizard will take you through the various options available for creating "
"tunnels in I2P."
msgstr ""
"Ta vodnik vas bo vodil skozi različne možnosti za ustvarjanje tuneljev v I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:293
msgid ""
"The first thing to decide is whether you want to create a server or a client "
"tunnel."
msgstr ""
"Prva stvar, ki jo morate odločiti, je, ali želite ustvariti strežniški ali "
"odjemalniški tunelj."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:294
msgid ""
"If you need to connect to a remote service, such as an IRC server inside I2P "
"or a code repository, then you will require a CLIENT tunnel."
msgstr ""
"Če morate povezati z oddaljeno storitev, kot je IRC strežnik v I2P ali "
"repozitorij kode, boste potrebovali ODJEMALNIŠKI tunelj."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:295
msgid ""
"On the other hand, if you wish to host a service for others to connect to "
"you'll need to create a SERVER tunnel."
msgstr ""
"S druge strani, če želite gostiti storitev za druge, da se povežejo do vas, "
"boste morali ustvariti STREŽNIŠKI tunelj."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:297
msgid "Server Tunnel"
msgstr "Strežniški tunelj"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:299
msgid "Client Tunnel"
msgstr "Odjemalniški tunelj"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:316
msgid "There are several types of tunnels to choose from:"
msgstr "Izberite med večjim številom tipov tuneljev:"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:324
msgid "Basic tunnel for connecting to a single service inside I2P."
msgstr "Osnovni tunelj za povezavo z eno storitev v I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:325
#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:350
msgid ""
"Try this if none of the tunnel types below fit your requirements, or you "
"don't know what type of tunnel you need."
msgstr ""
"Poskusite to, če noben od spodnjih tipov tuneljev ne ustreza vašim zahtevam, "
"ali če ne veste, katere vrste tunelja potrebujete."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:327
msgid "Tunnel that acts as an HTTP proxy for reaching eepsites inside I2P."
msgstr "Tunelj, ki deluje kot HTTP proxy za dostop do eepsite-jev v I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:328
msgid ""
"Set your browser to use this tunnel as an http proxy, or set your "
"\"http_proxy\" environment variable for command-line applications in GNU/"
"Linux."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite svoj brskalnik, da uporablja ta tunelj kot http proxy, ali "
"nastavite okoljsko spremenljivko \"http_proxy\" za ukazne vrstice v GNU/"
"Linux."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:329
msgid ""
"Websites outside I2P can also be reached if an HTTP proxy within I2P is "
"known."
msgstr ""
"Spletne strani izven I2P so tudi dosegljive, če je znano HTTP proxy v I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:331
msgid "Customised client tunnel specific for IRC connections."
msgstr "Prilagojen odjemalniški tunelj, poseben za IRC povezave."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:332
msgid ""
"With this tunnel type, your IRC client will be able to connect to an IRC "
"network inside I2P."
msgstr ""
"Z tipom tunelja bodo vaši IRC odjemalci lahko povezani z IRC omrežjem v I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:333
msgid ""
"Each IRC network in I2P that you wish to connect to will require its own "
"tunnel. (See Also, SOCKS IRC)"
msgstr ""
"Vsako IRC omrežje v I2P, s katerim želite povezati, bo potrebovalo svoj "
"lasten tunelj. (Poglejte tudi, SOCKS IRC)"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:335
msgid "A tunnel that implements the SOCKS protocol."
msgstr "Tunelj, ki implementira protokol SOCKS."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:336
msgid ""
"This enables both TCP and UDP connections to be made through a SOCKS "
"outproxy within I2P."
msgstr "To omogoča vzpostavitev povezav TCP in UDP skozi SOCKS outproxy v I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:338
msgid ""
"A client tunnel implementing the SOCKS protocol, which is customised for "
"connecting to IRC networks."
msgstr ""
"Odjemalniški tunelj, ki implementira protokol SOCKS, prilagojen za povezavo "
"z IRC omrežji."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:339
msgid ""
"With this tunnel type, IRC networks in I2P can be reached by typing the I2P "
"address into your IRC client, and configuring the IRC client to use this "
"SOCKS tunnel."
msgstr ""
"Z tipom tunelja so IRC omrežja v I2P dosegljiva, če vpišete I2P naslov v vaš "
"IRC odjemalca, in konfigurirate IRC odjemalca, da uporabi ta SOCKS tunelj."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:340
msgid ""
"This means that only one I2P tunnel is required rather than a separate "
"tunnel per IRC network."
msgstr ""
"To pomeni, da je potreben le en I2P tunelj, namesto ločenega tunelja za "
"vsako IRC omrežje."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:341
msgid ""
"IRC networks outside I2P can also be reached if a SOCKS outproxy within I2P "
"is known, though it depends on whether or not the outproxy has been blocked "
"by the IRC network."
msgstr ""
"IRC omrežja izven I2P so tudi dosegljiva, če je znano SOCKS outproxy v I2P, "
"vendar to zavisi od tega, ali je outproxy blokiran s strani IRC omrežja."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:349
msgid "A basic server tunnel for hosting a generic service inside I2P."
msgstr "Osnovni strežniški tunelj za gostiteljstvo splošne storitve v I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:352
msgid "A server tunnel that is customised for HTTP connections."
msgstr "Strežniški tunelj, prilagojen za povezave HTTP."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:353
msgid "Use this tunnel type if you want to host an eepsite."
msgstr "Uporabite ta tip tunelja, če želite gostiti eepsite."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:355
msgid "A customised server tunnel for hosting IRC networks inside I2P."
msgstr "Prilagojen strežniški tunelj za gostiteljstvo IRC omrežij v I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:356
msgid ""
"Usually, a separate tunnel needs to be created for each IRC server that is "
"to be accessible inside I2P."
msgstr ""
"Običajno je potreben ločen tunelj za vsak IRC strežnik, ki je dosegljiv v "
"I2P."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:362
msgid "Select tunnel type"
msgstr "Izberite vrsto tunelja"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:394
msgid "Choose a name and description for your tunnel."
msgstr "Izberite ime in opis za vaš tunelj."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:395
msgid ""
"These can be anything you want - they are just for ease of identifying the "
"tunnel in the routerconsole."
msgstr ""
"To lahko vstavite kar koli želite - to je samo za olajšanje identifikacije "
"tunelja v konzoli maršrutera."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:428
msgid ""
"If you know of any outproxies for this type of tunnel (either HTTP or "
"SOCKS), fill them in below."
msgstr ""
"Če znate kakšne outproxy-je za ta tip tunelja (HTTP ali SOCKS), jih vpišite "
"spodaj."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:429
msgid "Separate multiple proxies with commas."
msgstr "Ločite večje število proxy-jev z vejicami."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:433
msgid ""
"List of I2P outproxy destinations, separated with commas (e.g. "
"proxy1.i2p,proxy2.i2p)"
msgstr ""
"Seznam destinacij outproxy-jev I2P, ločen z vejicami (npr. "
"proxy1.i2p,proxy2.i2p)"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:451
msgid ""
"Type in the I2P destination of the service that this client tunnel should "
"connect to."
msgstr ""
"Vpišite destinacijo I2P storitve, do katere bi moral ta odjemalniški tunelj "
"povezati."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:452
msgid ""
"This could be the full Base64 destination key, or an I2P URL from your "
"address book."
msgstr ""
"To lahko je celoten ključ destinacije Base64, ali pa I2P URL iz vašega "
"imenika."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:456
msgid "Enter a b64 or .i2p address here"
msgstr "Vpišite b64 ali .i2p naslov tukaj"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:480
msgid ""
"This is the IP that your service is running on, this is usually on the same "
"machine so 127.0.0.1 is autofilled."
msgstr ""
"To je IP, na katerem deluje vaša storitev, to je običajno na istem stroju, "
"zato je samodejno vneseno 127.0.0.1."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:505
msgid "This is the port that the service is accepting connections on."
msgstr "To so vrata, na katerih sprejema povezave storitev."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:529
msgid "This is the port that the client tunnel will be accessed from locally."
msgstr "To so vrata, od koder bo odjemalniški tunelj dostopen lokalno."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:553
msgid ""
"How do you want this tunnel to be accessed? By just this machine, your "
"entire subnet, or external internet?"
msgstr ""
"Kako želite, da se ta tunelj dostopa? Samo z tem strokom, celotno podmrežjo, "
"ali z zunanjo interneto?"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:554
msgid "You will most likely want to just allow 127.0.0.1"
msgstr "Verjetno boste želeli le dopustiti 127.0.0.1"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:601
msgid ""
"The I2P router can automatically start this tunnel for you when the router "
"is started."
msgstr ""
"Maršruter I2P lahko ta tunelj samodejno zažene, ko se maršruter zagnal."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:602
msgid ""
"This can be useful for frequently-used tunnels (especially server tunnels), "
"but for tunnels that are only used occasionally it would mean that the I2P "
"router is creating and maintaining unnecessary tunnels."
msgstr ""
"To je uporabno za pogosto uporabljene tunelje (osebno strežniške tunelje), "
"vendar za tunelje, ki se uporabljajo le povsod, bi to pomenilo, da maršruter "
"I2P ustvarja in vzdržuje nepotrebnih tuneljev."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:629
msgid "The wizard has now collected enough information to create your tunnel."
msgstr "Vodnik je zdaj zbral dovolj informacij za ustvarjanje vašega tunelja."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:630
msgid ""
"Upon clicking the Save button below, the wizard will set up the tunnel, and "
"take you back to the main I2PTunnel page."
msgstr ""
"Po kliku na gumb Shrani spodaj bo vodnik nastavil tunelj in te vrnal nazaj "
"na glavno stran I2PTunnel."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:634
msgid ""
"Because you chose to automatically start the tunnel when the router starts, "
"you don't have to do anything further."
msgstr ""
"Ker ste izbrali, da se tunelj samodejno zažene, ko se maršruter zagnal, ni "
"potrebno storiti nič drugega."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:635
msgid "The router will start the tunnel once it has been set up."
msgstr "Maršruter bo zaželel tunelj, ko bo bil nastavljen."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:639
msgid ""
"Because you chose not to automatically start the tunnel, you will have to "
"manually start it."
msgstr ""
"Ker ste izbrali, da se tunelj ne zažene samodejno, ga boste morali zažeti "
"ročno."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:640
msgid ""
"You can do this by clicking the Start button on the main page which "
"corresponds to the new tunnel."
msgstr ""
"To lahko storite tako, da kliknete na gumb Zaženi na glavni strani, ki se "
"nanaša na nov tunelj."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:645
msgid "Below is a summary of the options you chose:"
msgstr "Spodaj je pregled možnosti, ki jih ste izbrali:"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:676
msgid "Tunnel description"
msgstr "Opis tunelja"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:700
msgid "Binding address"
msgstr "Naslov vezave"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:708
msgid "Tunnel port"
msgstr "Vrata tunelja"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:746
msgid ""
"Alongside these basic settings, there are a number of advanced options for "
"tunnel configuration."
msgstr ""
"Ob teh osnovnih nastavitvah obstajajo številne napredne možnosti za "
"konfiguracijo tunelja."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:747
msgid ""
"The wizard will set reasonably sensible default values for these, but you "
"can view and/or edit these by clicking on the tunnel's name in the main "
"I2PTunnel page."
msgstr ""
"Vodnik bo za te nastavitve razumno in smiselne privzete vrednosti, vendar "
"jih lahko ogledate in/ali uredite tako, da kliknete na ime tunelja na glavni "
"strani I2PTunnel."

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:765
msgid "Cancel the wizard and return to Tunnel Manager home page"
msgstr "Prekliči vodnika in vrni se na domačo stran Upravitelja tuneljev"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:773
msgid "Return to previous page"
msgstr "Vrni se na prejšnjo stran"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:776
msgid "Previous"
msgstr "Prejšnja"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:785
msgid "Save tunnel configuration"
msgstr "Shrani konfiguracijo tunelja"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:788
msgid "Save Tunnel"
msgstr "Shrani Tunelj"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:794
msgid "Finish Wizard and review tunnel settings"
msgstr "Končaj vodnika in preglej nastavitve tunelja"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:797
msgid "Finish"
msgstr "Končaj"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:803
msgid "Advance to next page"
msgstr "Napreduj na naslednjo stran"

#: ../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/i2ptunnel/jsp/wizard_jsp.java:806
msgid "Next"
msgstr "Naslednja"
